data.meta_description: 30.10.2023 - Steven was an American film editor known for his collaborations with directors Alfonso Cuarón and Barry Sonnenfeld. Weisberg collaborated with Cuarón on A Little Princess (1995), Great Expectations (1998) and Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (2004); with Sonnenfeld on the 2001 Fox pilot for The Tick, Big Trouble (2002) and Men in Black II (2002); and with García on Mother and Child (2009) and Albert Nobbs (2011).
